## Exploring your Entra ID Tenant
- portal.azure.com
- entra.microsoft.com
- admin.microsoft.com

## About the Free Azure Subscription

## Create and Manage Entra ID tenants
Manage Tenants > Create

## Create and Manage Azure Subscriptions
- Subscriptions = 1 Entra ID Tenant
**Subscription**: SUB-joeLoveless.com-AZ-104
**Tenant**: JoeLoveless - AZ-104 (joelovelessaz104.onmicrosoft.com)

## Configure Domains for Entra ID
- Entra ID > Custom Domain Names
- TXT or MX Record
- Domain Registrar
- **Domain**: joeloveless.dev

## Create and Manage User Identities
- Entra ID > New User
- Delete User > Mike Smith > Deleted Users
  - Allows you to restore the account.

## Bulk Create User Identities
- users > Bulk Operations
  - Bulk Create
  - Bulk Invite
  - Bulk Delete
- CSV file

## Register an Application in Entra ID
- Entra ID > App Registrations
  - Single tenant
  - Multi Tenant
  - Multi Tenant and Personal
  - Personal
- App-JoeLoveless.dev-FinanceApp
- API Permissions
  - Delegated
  - Application
- App Roles
  - Can configure permissions on who can use the apps and their roles (read, read/write, etc)
- Enterprise Applications
  - Users and Groups
    - Who can access the App

## Configure Managed Identities (System Assigned)
- More secure than Application Registration
- VM > Security > Identity > System-Assigned (On)
```powershell
az login --identity
```
- Don't need to use a username and password

